Step 1: Add MarketplaceStep 2: Browse PluginsStep 3: Install &amp; Use <p>Add the Talent Factory marketplace to your <code>.claude/settings.json</code>:</p> JSON<pre><code>{
  "extraKnownMarketplaces": {
    "talent-factory": {
      "source": {
        "source": "github",
        "repo": "talent-factory/claude-plugins"
      }
    }
  }
}
</code></pre> <p>Open Claude Code and use the plugin command:</p> Bash<pre><code>claude
/plugin
</code></pre> <p>Select "Browse Plugins" → "talent-factory"</p> <p>Choose plugins to install, then use commands like:</p> Bash<pre><code>/commit
/create-pr
/create-prd
/review
</code></pre>

JSON<pre><code>{
  "enabledPlugins": {
    "education@talent-factory": true,
    "code-quality@talent-factory": true,
    "git-workflow@talent-factory": true
  }
}
</code></pre>

